# CVEs in Expo CLI toolchain dependencies (@xmldom/xmldom, node-tar).
# These packages are used only by Expo's build tooling (never shipped to production).
# Fixing requires downgrading to Expo 49 which breaks the SDK.
# Tracked and will be resolved when Expo SDK 52+ ships patched versions.
# Dependency vulnerability scanning for npm packages is handled by Snyk + npm audit in CI.
